# Code owners for callendulla.
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# These owners get auto-requested for review on every PR.
# Order matters — last match wins.

# Default: everything goes to @jetmil
*                       @jetmil

